videoDetails.Title: WAR THUNDER HATES THIS PLANE - A-10A in War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
If you're looking to get some GE or a Premium, please use a creators link to support then and get a free decal.  Here's mine:  https://store.gaijin.net/catalog.php?category=WarThunder&partner=Oddbawz&partner_val=2bpa5qx4

The A-10A in War Thunder is a Premium Strike Aircraft for the US Tech Tree.  Armed with the famous GAU-12 30mm cannon but also the thing that makes it really devastating is the AGM-65B Mavericks.  The problem is, the seekers on the Mavericks right now are an absolute joke!

The AGM-65B seeker decides what it wants to do.  It won't lock or it will lock but not track the target.  It'll just start tracking a spec of dust flying through the air... who knows what it's doing but it's really frustrating.

The A-10A is still kinda fun but it's at a battle rating where you don't get much use from the main attraction which is the 30mm cannon.  10.3 is a rough spot for USA in Ground Realistic and that certainly doesn't help this plane.

The golden era of the Warthog is gone! :(
